data.description: You'll love this move-in ready condo with tons of new updates! NEW flooring, NEW stainless steel appliances, NEW modern fixtures, NEW beautiful granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, NEW toilets and NEW fresh paint! Lovely vinyl wood flooring throughout, spacious living area and gorgeous eat-in kitchen with pantry. 3 upper level bedrooms all with ceiling fans including a large primary suite. Light and Bright! Fantastic resort-like amenities including a community swimming pool, playground, exercise room, sauna, meeting room and event space. Schedule your showing today!
